Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.70,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:02.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}對著無法起飛的螺旋槳做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:06.90,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝著天空的另一半抬頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.01,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光著腳丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:14.45,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:21.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}無論誤會與否 就是對生活充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:34.89,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的寶物 藏起來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:43.49,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也無法發現那顆深藏起來的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.49,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕嚕咕嚕轉上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.60,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:55.63,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:59.34,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢想一定會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:10.87,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們要永遠在一起哦
